      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 00:01:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新政府或放宽限制，世界农作物贸易关注印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/world-crop-trade-eyes-india-as-new-government-may-relax-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月新政府上台后，农业市场正在关注印度贸易政策的潜在变化，这可能会对全球粮食价格产生重大影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-01/world-crop-trade-eyes-india-as-new-government-may-relax-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
